- Exactly matches design
- Precise CSS values

How to use:
- "Convert design to pixel-perfect CSS"
- "Make this pixel-perfect match"

DARK MODE
---------
How to use:
- "Add dark mode support"
- "Create dark mode CSS variables"

A11Y (ACCESSIBILITY)
